furicam (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release of FuriCam
  * H.264/MP4 video recording with configurable bitrate
  * Resolution picker with per-camera memory
  * JPEG quality adjustment
  * Grid overlay and level indicator (sensorfw accelerometer)
  * Camera resume on focus change

